##############################################################
                           README
                SDSU-v2/src/simulator/hydrom
                                                     May.,2009
                                                 Hiro Masunaga
                      Hydrospheric Atmospheric Research Center
                                             Nagoya University
##############################################################

This directory contains subroutines used for calculating the
hydrometeor radiative properties, called by the microwave
radiometer, radar, and visible/infrared simulators as well as
the Mie lookup table generator (../../src/MieLUT/).

##################### FILE LIST #######################

- README-hydrom (this file)
	ASCII document to describe the content of this directory.

-------------- Fortran source codes -------------------

- MCRPparameters.f90
	MCRPparameters: F90 module for the hydrometer radiative properties
	                including the PSD/DSD function (psd_func).
- df_mie_melt.f90
	df_mie_melt: calculates the radiative properties in the melting layer.
- gammaf.f90
	gammaf, gammln: calculates gamma function.
- heymsplatt.f90:
	heymsplatt: obtains an cloud ice PSD based on the Heymsfield and 
	            Platt (1984) parameterization
- iceoptic.f90
	iceoptic: obtains the ice optical properties at microwave frequencies.
- mg_ell.f90
	mg_ellips: Maxwell-Garnett routine for elliptical inclusions
- microp_set.f90
	microp_set: user interface for microphysical setup
- mie_cldi.f90
	mie_cldi: microwave Mie calculation code for cloud ice
- mie_cldi_vir.f90
	mie_cldi_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for cloud ice
- mie_cldw.f90 
	mie_cldw: microwave Mie calculation code for cloud water
- mie_cldw_vir.f90
	mie_cldw_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for cloud water
- mie_grpl.f90
	mie_grpl: microwave Mie calculation code for cloud graupel
- mie_grpl_vir.f90
	mie_grpl_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for cloud graupel
- mie_hail.f90
	mie_hail: microwave Mie calculation code for cloud hail
- mie_hail_vir.f90
	mie_hail_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for cloud hail
- mie_melt.f90:
	mie_melt: computes the radiative properties of melting particles.
	          Called by "df_mie_melt".
- mie_rain.f90
	mie_rain: microwave Mie calculation code for snow
- mie_rain_vir.f90
	mie_rain_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for snow
- mie_snow.f90
	mie_snow: microwave Mie calculation code for snow
- mie_snow_vir.f90
	mie_snow_vir: visible/IR Mie calculation code for snow
- mie_sphere.f90
	mie_sphere: obtains the radiative properties of particles based
	            on the Mie theory. 
- mie_sphere_vir.f90
	mie_sphere_vir: an extended version of 'mie_sphere' with phase
	                function included for use by visible/IR simulation.
- mklab_lut.f90
	mklab_lut: labels the lookup tables for microwave and radar simulations
	mklab_lut_vir: labels the lookup tables for visible/IR simulation
- refind_vir.f90: 
	watrefind_vir: obtains the visible/IR refractive index of water
	icerefind_vir: obtains the visible/IR refractive index of ice
- watoptic.f90
	watopic: obtains the water optical properties at microwave frequencies.
